<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Merchant Registration</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #FF6B35;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF6B35;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #FF6B35;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .business-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35;
        }
        .business-info h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .business-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .business-info strong {
            color: #FF6B35;
        }
        .action-required {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .action-required h3 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FF6B35;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .urgent {
            color: #d63031;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Indians in Ghana</div>
            <p>Community Business Directory</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>üè¢ New Merchant Registration Alert</h1>
            
            <p>Dear Admin,</p>
            
            <p>A new merchant has registered and is awaiting approval for the Indians in Ghana Business Directory.</p>

            <div class="business-info">
                <h3>üìã Business Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Business Name:</strong> {{businessName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Owner Name:</strong> {{fullName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
                <p><strong>Category:</strong> {{businessCategory}}</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{businessLocation}}</p>
                <p><strong>Registration Date:</strong> {{registrationDate}}</p>
                {{#if businessDescription}}
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{businessDescription}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="action-required">
                <h3>‚ö° Action Required</h3>
                <p class="urgent">This merchant registration requires administrative approval.</p>
                <p>Please review the merchant details and approve or reject the application.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{adminDashboardUrl}}" class="button">Review Merchant Application</a>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: #e8f4fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #0066cc; margin-top: 0;">üìå Next Steps</h3>
                <ul style="color: #333; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Login to the admin dashboard</li>
                    <li>Navigate to "Merchant Applications"</li>
                    <li>Review business details and documentation</li>
                    <li>Approve or reject with appropriate feedback</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for maintaining the quality of our business directory.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Indians in Ghana Platform</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from the Indians in Ghana platform.</p>
            <p>If you have questions, please contact technical support.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <small>¬© 2025 Indians in Ghana. All rights reserved.</small>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>